SUPERMARKET SALES ANALYSIS REPORT

Objective:
Analyze sales performance, customer behavior, and product trends.

Key Findings:
• Product line performance analyzed
• Customer purchasing behavior evaluated
• Revenue trends identified
• Payment preferences studied

Recommendations:
• Increase inventory for top-selling products
• Focus on high-performing cities
• Optimize promotional campaigns

Conclusion:
The analysis identified major revenue drivers and opportunities for business growth.
